---
title: Barbecue Beef Meatloaves with Potato Wedges, Cabbage Slaw, and Alabama White Sauce
description: In case you’re not from Alabama, the home of white barbecue sauce, let us give you a tip: this is the sauce you’ll want to put on everything. Based around mayonnaise with mustard and vinegar mixed in for a kick, it balances creamy and tangy flavors in a way that few other sauces do. The barbecue-spiced mini beef meatloaves in this recipe are the perfect canvas for drizzling all that goodness onto. Plus, this dish comes with potato wedges and a red cabbage slaw on the side—what’s not to love?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/barbecue-beef-meatloaves-574b5e67.jpg
